import folium
m = folium.Map(
    location=[0, 15],
    zoom_start=1, min_zoom=1, max_bounds=True,
    #width=1000, height=525,
    #control_scale=True,  # Adds distance scale in lower left corner
    tiles=None,
)

image = 'OPTA.tif'


img = folium.raster_layers.ImageOverlay(
    name="DNI",
    image=image,
    bounds=[[-55, -180], [60, 180]],
    #opacity=0.6,
    #interactive=True,
    #cross_origin=False,
    zindex=1,
)
img.add_to(m)
folium.LayerControl().add_to(m)

  • http://hanschen.org/koppen
